            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Petrus">Pietro</name></persName> figlio di
                                <persName><name ref="Signorectus">Signoretto</name></persName> e la
                        moglie <persName><name ref="Ingerada">Ingalrada</name></persName> del
                            <persName key="#Judge">fu <name ref="Sigefredus"
                            >Sighifridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">giudice</rs>, con il consenso del marito e mundualdo
                        Pietro, vendono a <persName key="#Abbots"><name ref="Leo"
                            >Leone</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abate</rs> del <rs key="#Monasteries">monastero</rs> di
                            <orgName key="#Houses #Monasteries #Hospitals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/71">San Ponziano</orgName> di <placeName
                            ref="#places/4">Lucca</placeName>, e a <persName><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Giovanni</name></persName>, rector de <rs key="#Hospitals"
                            >hospitale</rs> suprascripti Sancti Pontiani, quartam portionem di una
                            <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs> et res massaricias posta in loco et finibus
                            <placeName ref="#places/3305">Stabbiano ubi dicitur a la
                            Leccia</placeName>, tenuta da <persName><name ref="Stephanus"
                                >Stefano</name></persName> massarium, que nobis per <rs
                            key="#Venditio">cartula</rs> scripta ex manibus del <rs key="#Notary"
                            >notaio imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Ildebrandus">Ildebrando</name></persName>
                        in loco pignoris ex comparatione obvenit da <persName key="#Notary"><name
                                ref="Raginmundus">Raimondo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notaio</rs> del <persName>fu <name ref="Petrus"
                                key="#Notary">Pietro</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notaio</rs>, ricevendo <rs
                            key="#Meritum/launechild #Jewels">meritum anulum unum aureo</rs> dal <rs
                            key="#Other_clerics">chierico</rs>
                        <persName key="#Other_clerics"><name ref="Cicco">Cigo</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName>. Chiedono al <rs
                            key="#Writer #Notary">notaio imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Cuneradus"
                            >Corrado</name></persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum Luca. <rs
                            key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori: <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Paulus">Paolo</name></persName> di <persName
                            key="#Other_clerics"><name ref="Cicco">Cigo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Signorectus">Signoretto</name></persName> del <persName>fu
                                <name ref="Iohannes">Giovanni</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Rodelandus">Rodilando</name></persName> di <persName
                            key="#Judge"><name ref="Antonius/Sapiebonus">Antonio</name> detto
                            Sapiebono</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs>. </ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                        <p>Degli Azzi Vitelleschi, 2, n. 67, pp. 22-23.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
